Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pydirstat
Version: 0.9.14
Summary: Show statistics informations for a directory in HTML, SVG, or Flash.
Home-page: http://pydirstat.berlios.de/
Author: Arthibus Gissehel
Author-email: public-pds-setup@giss.ath.cx
License: UNKNOWN
Description: pyDirStat is a small tool to view statistical information
        about a directory. It will generate a view of all files contained in a
        directory (and subdirectories) with rectangles. Each rectangle area is
        proportional to file size.
        It's a perfect tool to view disk usage with graphics.
